<div class="content-section-apply container" id="apply">
  <h1 class="center">apply</h1>
  <h2>what we're looking for</h2>
  <p>starting a food truck is no small task, we get that. we're looking for cooks out there who get that too.
    <div class="row"> 
      <div class="col-lg-3">
        <h2>can you cook?</h2>
        <p>of course, we want to know if you have the culinary chops. we are looking for chefs or senior suos chefs to apply to this program. not there yet? cut your teeth for a little longer, and we'll be waiting when you're done. 
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h2>blood, sweat and tears</h2>
        <p>starting a business is tough, we know. we want chefs who are going to put in the time and the elbow grease to get into the black.  
        <p>we're invested in your success, we want you to be invested in ours. that means being flexible, reasonable, and at times, a little outside the box. 
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
